        <briefdescription>
<para>This function is the interrupt handler for the MPEG TS MUX core driver. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This handler clears the pending interrupt and determines if the source is frame done signal. If yes, calls the registered callback function.</para><para>The application is responsible for connecting this function to the interrupt system.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the core instance that just interrupted.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
